        <item>
            <title>Version 0.8.2</title>
            <pubDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 17:27:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.8.2</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.8.2</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>New: rename any tab &#8212; double-click a tab in the sidebar to give it a custom name. Enter or click away saves, Esc cancels, and saving an empty name goes back to the page&#8217;s own title. Custom names survive restarts and moving a tab to another window.</li>
                    <li>Improved: double-clicking to rename a tab, bookmark, or folder now preselects the current name, so you can just type the new one.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
              url="https://github.com/dep/synapse-browser/releases/download/0.8.2/Synapse.Browser-0.8.2-universal.dmg"
