        <item>
            <title>Version 0.8.0</title>
            <pubDate>Sat, 18 Jul 2026 12:13:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>0.8.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.8.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>New: split-screen views &#8212; Cmd+D tiles a new pane beside the page, Cmd+Shift+D stacks one below; panes tile free-form with no limit.</li>
                    <li>New: Cmd-click a sidebar tab or pin to open it in a split next to the current pane; the focused pane glows blue and each pane has a corner &#215; to untile it.</li>
                    <li>Changed: Bookmark This Page moved from Cmd+D to Cmd+B.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
            <enclosure
              url="https://github.com/dep/synapse-browser/releases/download/0.8.0/Synapse.Browser-0.8.0-universal.dmg"
