            <sparkle:version>0.7.0</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>0.7.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>New: Cmd+N opens a new window &#8212; a lightweight workspace with its own tabs.</li>
                    <li>New: drag a tab out of the sidebar past the window edge to move it into its own window &#8212; no reload, playing media keeps playing.</li>
                    <li>Menus, find, tab cycling, and the address bar all act on the window you're using.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
