            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>The sidebar scrollbar now matches the dark theme instead of intermittently rendering as a white system scrollbar.</li>
                    <li>Alt+Cmd+Up/Down now steps through pins, bookmarks, and tabs — the same order as Alt+Tab.</li>
